WEBVTT

00:14:29.035 --> 00:14:31.216
RNG: Ah, ne nadam se.

00:14:31.216 --> 00:14:33.273
SP: Ipak, postao sam uvjeren

00:14:33.273 --> 00:14:34.984
da je razum bolji anđeo

00:14:34.984 --> 00:14:36.556
koji zaslužuje najveće zasluge

00:14:36.556 --> 00:14:39.210
za moralni napredak naše vrste

00:14:39.210 --> 00:14:41.325
i da je u njemu najveća nada

00:14:41.325 --> 00:14:44.141
za nastavak moralnog napretka 
u budućnosti.

00:14:44.141 --> 00:14:46.043
RNG: I ako vi, naši prijatelji,

00:14:46.043 --> 00:14:48.723
nađete manu u ovom argumentu,

00:14:48.723 --> 00:14:52.045
upamtite da ćete ovisiti o razumu

00:14:52.045 --> 00:14:53.416
kako biste to istakli.

00:14:53.416 --> 00:14:56.130
Hvala vam.
SP: Hvala vam.

00:14:56.130 --> 00:15:03.125
(Pljesak)